        <para>
            <emph type="boldundersc">WIRING INFORMATION</emph>
        </para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>Customer provides a remote-mounted switch that is wired into the pin labeled
                    Remote_Engine_Speed_Sw_Input on the Black 23-pin input connector on the Remote Power Module (See
                    ICAP or the Diamond Logic&#8482; Builder software for correct pin location).
                </para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Customer provides the wiring from the pin labeled UTILITY_EMERGENCY_PUMP_Output on the Brown 8-pin
                    Remote Power Module output connector, to a customer-supplied relay. From that relay, a wire runs to
                    the emergency pump (See ICAP or the Diamond Logic&#8482; Builder software for correct pin location).
                </para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
